Question No.: 577

Title: Employee Bonus

Difficulty: Easy

Topic: SQL (LEFT JOIN, WHERE, NULL Handling)

SELECT e.name, b.bonus
FROM Employee e
LEFT JOIN Bonus b
ON e.empId = b.empId
WHERE b.bonus < 1000 OR b.bonus IS NULL;
